## Task

Wire the differential drill into the main read path by updating `resolve_chunk_info()` and its callers to pass the old manifest when available.

### Current flow (crates/rift-client/src/view.rs:302-340)

```rust
async fn resolve_chunk_info(
    &self,
    handle: Uuid,
    root_hash: &Blake3Hash,
    merkle_root: &[u8],
    file_size: u64,
) -> Result<(Vec<ResolvedLeaf>, Vec<u64>, bool), FsError> {
    // 1. Try cached manifest → if root matches, return immediately (no drill at all)
    // 2. Otherwise → call resolve_merkle_tree() which drills EVERYTHING
    if let Some(cache) = self.cache() {
